        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: add org deletion cascade",
        "body": "Closes #2516.\n\n## Summary\n- Adds an owner-only organization delete flow in account settings.\n- Soft-deletes org publishers and cascades org-owned skills plus packages/plugins out of public surfaces without hard-deleting publisher, membership, resource, or audit rows.\n- Extends account deletion so personal publisher resources and sole-owner org resources are hidden through the same soft-delete/deactivation path.\n- Adds focused backend/UI tests plus a local-auth Playwright e2e that deletes an org with one skill and one plugin and verifies both disappear from user-facing surfaces.\n- Updates durable org/security specs for the soft-delete invariant.\n\n## Tests\n- `VITE_CONVEX_URL=https://example.invalid bunx vitest run convex/publishers.test.ts convex/packages.public.test.ts convex/skills.banBatches.test.ts convex/users.test.ts src/routes/-settings.test.tsx`\n- `bun run ci:static`\n- `bun run ci:unit`\n- `bun run ci:types-build`\n- `PLAYWRIGHT_LOCAL_AUTH_CONVEX_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3310 PLAYWRIGHT_LOCAL_AUTH_CONVEX_SITE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3311 bun run test:pw:local-auth -- --project=chromium e2e/local-auth/delete-org-resources.pw.test.ts`\n- Proof MP4 run: `CLAWHUB_ORG_DELETE_PROOF_VIDEO=1 PLAYWRIGHT_LOCAL_AUTH_CONVEX_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3310 PLAYWRIGHT_LOCAL_AUTH_CONVEX_SITE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3311 bun run test:pw:local-auth -- --project=chromium e2e/local-auth/delete-org-resources.pw.test.ts`\n\n## Proof\n- Local MP4 artifact: `.artifacts/org-deletion-proof/org-deletion-resources-20260605-1356.mp4`\n",
